### Product positioning (constraint-driven)
- Build a **web-first** creator monetization platform with:
  - subscriptions (multi-plan)
  - PPV purchases (posts + messages)
  - wallet top-up
  - tipping (including tip goals)
  - messaging (real-time updates)
  - notifications (in-app + email + **web push**)
  - reels/stories
  - live streaming (**Mux Live**)
  - discovery (categories, tags, search, trending)

### Non-functional requirements (must-have)
- Security: access control for locked media, payment integrity, rate limiting on sensitive endpoints.
- Consistency: UI layout + nav must be stable across all routes; coherent empty/loading states.
- Observability: consistent error responses + logs; no silent failures.
- Quality gates: TypeScript + ESLint clean for touched files; QA plan executable.

### Open questions (resolved by human)
- Live streaming provider: **Mux Live**
- Push notifications: **Web Push only**

